translations.template.content.json_architecture:
Memory bank documents are stored in JSON format with the following structure:

```json
{
  "schema": "memory_document_v2",
  "metadata": {
    "id": "unique-identifier",
    "title": "Document Title",
    "documentType": "document-type",
    "path": "relative-path",
    "tags": ["related-tags"],
    "lastModified": "last-modified-date",
    "createdAt": "creation-date",
    "version": 1
  },
  "content": {
    // Document content
  }
}
```

